description: [``botocore``] Fixed a typo in description field.

[``botocore``] With this release, Amazon EC2 Auto Scaling groups, EC2 Fleet, and Spot Fleet improve the default price protection behavior of attribute-based instance type selection of Spot Instances, to consistently select from a wide range of instance types.
